title: Faces of LoL #1
body:
http://imgur.com/lugC6bS When the game starts out and everyone's happy, but then someone feeds the enemy Katarina a double.

http://imgur.com/H5tcF96 When you're support and you save your ADC from the whole Enemy Team and still get out alive.

http://imgur.com/dFi4Ai2 When the fed Fizz on your team goes HAM. (The fifth person is the enemy support, and the rest is Fizz's team)
